msgid "[[!meta title=\"Chat\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Xat\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Join our XMPP chat room to ask questions about Tails."
msgstr "Uniu-vos a la nostra sala de xat XMPP per fer preguntes sobre Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To do so, you need an XMPP account. You can sign up for an XMPP account at "
"[Disroot](https://disroot.org/services/xmpp)  or any other XMPP account "
"provider."
msgstr ""
"Per fer-ho, necessiteu un compte XMPP. Podeu registrar-vos per obtenir un "
"compte XMPP a [Disroot](https://disroot.org/services/xmpp) o qualsevol altre "
"proveïdor de comptes XMPP."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Then configure your preferred instant messaging client, for example [[Pidgin|"
"http://www.pidgin.im/]], which runs on Windows, GNU/Linux, and macOS, to "
"connect to:"
msgstr ""
"A continuació, configureu el vostre client de missatgeria instantània "
"preferit, per exemple [[Pidgin|http://www.pidgin.im/]], que s'executa a "
"Windows, GNU/Linux i macOS, per connectar-vos a:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<ul>\n"
"  <li>Room: <code>tails</code></li>\n"
"  <li>Server: <code>chat.disroot.org</code></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
msgstr ""
"<ul>\n"
"  <li>Sala: <code>tails</code></li>\n"
"  <li>Servidor: <code>chat.disroot.org</code></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"

#~ msgid "Room: `tails`"
#~ msgstr "Sala: `tails`"

#~ msgid "Server: `chat.disroot.org`"
